Package: netcfg
Version: 0.1.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: netcfg authors
Depends: iproute2
Conflicts: netplan.io
Replaces: netplan.io
Provides: netplan.io
Description: Network configuration tool with netns support
 netcfg is a network configuration tool that is compatible with netplan
 syntax and adds native support for network namespaces (netns).
 .
 It uses netlink directly for better performance and security.
 .
 Features:
  - Full netplan YAML compatibility
  - Native network namespace support
  - Bridge, bond, VLAN, VXLAN, macvlan support
  - Direct netlink API (no ip command dependency)
